    <h2>Our Aim</h2><br />
    <p id="">
        Funded by Creative New Zealand, Arts Murihiku aims to increase arts participation in the Southland,
        Queenstown, Glenorchy, Arrowtown, Tapanui and Heriot areas,
        support a new regional arts body and provide development
        training for artists and arts organisations. We’re here to help you, the artists and practitioners.
    </p>
    <img src="~/images/areas/south pan.jpg" height="40" width="300" alt="Avatar" class="imag"><br />
    <h2>Who are we?</h2><br />
    <p>We are a recently formed organisation who aim to engage the community and bring awareness to the arts
    of Southland. Our team of ethusiatic trustees and advocates are always willing to help the Artists of Southland
    and this new site is here to facillitate their needs and foster creativity and expression.</p>
  
